      "content": [
        {
          "type": "thinking",
          "thinking": "Now I can see which departments have exceeded their budget (cumulative_amount > annual_budget):\n\n1. D001 - 投资银行部: budget=230,395.17, cumulative=363,614.58 → exceeded\n2. D002 - 固定收益部: budget=107,785.42, cumulative=164,928.12 → exceeded\n3. D003 - 财富管理部: budget=109,772.07, cumulative=174,150.67 → exceeded\n4. D004 - 研究所: budget=264,890.39, cumulative=408,832.95 → exceeded\n5. D005 - 机构业务部: budget=278,540.94, cumulative=433,442.76 → exceeded\n6. D006 - 运营管理部: budget=340,961.75, cumulative=530,241.29 → exceeded\n7. D007 - 信息技术部: budget=301,500.00, cumulative=252,588.38 → within budget\n8. D008 - 合规风控部: budget=381,600.00, cumulative=297,095.29 → within budget\n9. D009 - 财务管理部: budget=191,300.00, cumulative=159,294.06 → within budget\n10. D010 - 人力资源部: budget=164,500.00, cumulative=139,536.39 → within budget\n\nSo D001 through D006 have cumulatively exceeded their annual budgets. This matches BUDGET-002 - departments exceeding their budget.\n\nAccording to policy \"08_budget_management.md\":\n- Article 2: Departments should incur expenses within their annual budget.\n- Article 3: After cumulative expenses reach 1.0x of annual budget, no further reimbursement should be allowed in principle.\n- Article 4: Special approval should be obtained if over-budget expenses are necessary.\n\nAnd \"01_expense_reimbursement_2025.md\" Article 13 also says: when department annual budget is insufficient, no further reimbursement. After budget usage reaches 1.0x of budget, expenses that are truly needed require special approval.\n\nSo the question is: \"异常BUDGET-002涉及哪些报销记录?\" - Which reimbursement records are involved in anomaly BUDGET-002?\n\nBUDGET-002 seems to be about department budget overspending. I need to find the actual expense records that were submitted after the budget was exhausted (the records that pushed the department over budget).\n\nLet me look at the expenses for the departments that exceeded their budgets to find the specific records. Let me start with D001 (投资银行部) which has exceeded its budget.",
          "signature": ""
        },
